  "Description": {
    "English": "A device that modulates standard starship communication signals to <span class=\"name name-technology\">enable the transport of matter</span> as well as data.<br><br>Starships fitted with such a device can send and receive products and substances to a user's exosuit over a <VAL_ON>long distance<>.",
